Create a global-brand quality logo for “Krish Accessories”, inspired by the simplicity and memorability of Amazon, Flipkart, Myntra, CRED, and other top international brands. 
The design must look human-crafted, intentional, premium, and perfect for a modern e-commerce + lifestyle accessories brand.

Core Concept:
Combine the ideas of a smile-curve (customer happiness like Amazon), a subtle shopping-cart motion element (Flipkart’s retail identity), and a smooth lifestyle loop (Myntra’s flow), all merged into a single iconic symbol that represents “K” and “A” together.

Symbol Requirements:
• Create a simple, bold, globally recognizable icon 
• Merge the letters “K” and “A” inside a single smooth flowing shape 
• Add a clean curved “smile/arrow” under the logo to represent:
 - customer happiness 
 - fast service 
 - forward movement 
• Integrate a minimal, abstract hint of a shopping cart handle or motion stroke
• Keep the symbol extremely simple and universal, avoiding AI-random shapes 
• Must work as an app icon, website logo, packaging, and offline signage 
• Strong silhouette, perfect symmetry, professional geometric balance 

Symbol Meaning (must be embedded visually):
• “K” = Krish 
• “A” = Accessories 
• Smile curve = happiness + fast delivery 
• Motion stroke = efficiency and trends 
• Loop flow = fashion, lifestyle, modernity 
• Abstract cart = online + offline shopping identity
